wiki.summary: "Fancy" is the fourth single from Iggy Azalea's debut studio album, The New Classic (2014). It features English singer-songwriter Charli XCX. The song is described as an electro-hop, electropop and pop rap song. It was written by Azalea and XCX, composed and produced by production team the Invisible Men, alongside additional producers The Arcade. Read more on Last.fm.
